reviewText: DVD did not come with booklet reference in the program.  I didn't like the pace - the exercise is introduced then done - prefer continuous exercise.  Also didn't like '2 sets of 15' with no break at all - it's really one set of 30.
Replacing an age old video from NIA.  Like it.
Product came in as promised.  On time and in great shape.  Now if it will just get me in great shape!
